  "texts": [
    "Our review suggests that while there are numerous works evaluating the opportunities in defensive applications of LLMs, there is a lack of research in examining the risks of offensive applications.",
    "We hope this study paves the way for future research to assess the associated risks introduced by the rise of LLMs in cybersecurity.Figure 1:1Figure 1: The present bar chart illustrates the distribution of studies mapped to each of the five elements of the NIST Cybersecurity Framework.",
    "Collected statistics indicate that the vast amount of studies are related to Protect and Detect functions emphasizing research gaps related to Identify, Respond and particularly Recover functions over collected publications.",
    "Table 1:1Classified publications concerning the defensive applications of LLMs.Paper Year NIST Framework Application"
  ]
}